# Product Images Directory

This directory contains high-quality product images for menu items.

## Image Guidelines
- Format: JPG, PNG, or SVG
- Recommended size: 800x800px (1:1 aspect ratio)
- Naming convention: {menu-item-slug}.jpg (e.g., americano.jpg, latte.jpg)
- Optimize images for web (compress without losing quality)
- Use high-quality, professional product photography

## Current Images
- default-coffee.svg - Default placeholder for all items (currently in use)

## Adding Product Images
1. Take or source high-quality product photos
2. Resize to 800x800px maintaining aspect ratio
3. Optimize for web (aim for < 200KB per image)
4. Name according to the menu item (lowercase, hyphenated)
5. Place in this directory

